Graph summary data

Usage

Arguments

Summary information with options

list

Examples


if (FALSE) { # \dontrun{

library(inti)
library(gsheet)

url <- paste0("https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/"
              , "15r7ZwcZZHbEgltlF6gSFvCTFA-CFzVBWwg3mFlRyKPs/edit#gid=338518609")
# browseURL(url)

fb <- gsheet2tbl(url)

info <- yupana_import(fb)

} # }
